<a id="products"></a>
<dt class="col-sm-1">Products</dt>

<dd class="col-sm-11">This page shows list of all active products present currently in database. Reference Code column is linked to product profile. Edit icon, <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-edit"></i> will take you directly to <Edit Product> form, where you can change all product attributes, except reference code. Optional "notes' field is only visible to you and can be used to store product-specific info. 
</dd>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<!-- Orders index page -->
<a id="orders"></a>
<dt class="col-sm-1">Orders</dt>

<dd class="col-sm-11">This page shows list of client orders, most recent first. #Products column shows number of different products bought, while #Items column signifies total number of items.  
Drop-down box at the top of the page allows you to filter orders by order number, total amount, date etc. Invoice and PO colums have links to download PO/Invoice in PDF format. Grand total at the bottom shows total value of all orders in Euros using current USD/EUR FX conversion rate shown in the footer.
</dd>

